&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;border:none;mso-padding-alt:31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt;
mso-border-shadow:yes&quot;&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Trebuchet MS&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Trebuchet MS&amp;quot;;
mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Trebuchet MS&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;Outra estrutura condicional semelhante à
estrutura &lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;se&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; é a &lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-style:normal&quot;&gt;escolha&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.
Ela pode ser comparada a um &lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;se&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
com diversos &lt;span class=&quot;SpellE&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;senao&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;
&lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;se&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt; e um possível &lt;span class=&quot;SpellE&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;senao&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.
Basicamente, usa-se uma variável de controle, a declara-se comparações de
igualdade a serem feitas sobre ela. Diferentemente do condicional &lt;i&gt;se&lt;/i&gt;,
apenas os tipos de dado &lt;span class=&quot;SpellE&quot;&gt;caracter&lt;/span&gt; e inteiro são
permitidos. Abaixo, dois códigos que executam a mesma tarefa: um usando um
bloco &lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-style:
normal&quot;&gt;se&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; e outro usando &lt;span class=&quot;GramE&quot;&gt;o &lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal&quot;&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-style:normal&quot;&gt;escolha&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
